==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Libertarian
<hw>Lib`er*ta"ri*an</hw> <pr>(-t⟦amac⟧"r⟦icr⟧*⟦ait⟧n)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Liberty</er>.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to
liberty, or to the doctrine of free will, as opposed to the doctrine of
necessity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Libertarian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Libertarian
<hw>Lib`er*ta"ri*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who holds to the
doctrine of free will.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Libertarianism</ent>⟦br⟧
